{"word":"ἀσθένεια","slug":"ἀσθένεια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀσϑένεια, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀσθενής\">ἀσθενής</a></el>; antonym <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δύναμις\">δύναμις</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘condition of debilitating illness’, <b><i>sickness, disease, disability</i> <a href='B:470 8:17'>Mt 8:17</a>; <a href='B:490 5:15'>Lk 5:15</a>; <a href='B:490 13:11'>13:11</a>; <a href='B:500 5:5'>J 5:5</a>;</b> <el>ἔχειν ἀ.</el> <i>be ill</i> <b><a href='B:510 28:9'>Ac 28:9</a>; <a href='B:550 4:13'>Gal 4:13</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘incapacity for functioning effectively because of some limitation or vulnerability’, <b><i>weakness, deficiency</i> <a href='B:530 15:43'>1 Cor 15:43</a>; <a href='B:540 11:30'>2 Cor 11:30</a>; <a href='B:540 12:5'>12:5</a>; <a href='B:540 13:4'>13:4</a>; <a href='B:650 4:15'>Hb 4:15</a>; <a href='B:650 5:2'>5:2</a>; <a href='B:650 7:28'>7:28</a>; <a href='B:650 11:34'>11:34</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:520 6:19'>Ro 6:19</a>; <a href='B:520 8:26'>8:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἀσήρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀσθενέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}